Silkroad Server Stats

Windows Requirements
Visual Studio 2010
Qt 5.1.1+
Boost

You will need to make sure that both the boost path and Qt plugin lib
paths are both setup correctly in the Visual C++ settings.

Linux Requirements
gcc/g++
Qt 5.1.1+
Boost

Debian Compile Guide
1. Install Qt SDK
apt-get install qt-sdk

2. Download the and install the latest Qt 5.1 release
http://qt-project.org/downloads

3. Install boost
apt-get install libboost-*

4. Open ServerStats\ServerStats.pro with the QtCreator

5. Ctrl + R